# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:14
translate chinese lisa0_b7252674:

    # "When I walk into the hallway, I can hear the TV on in the living room, playing the local news."
    "走进走廊时，我听到客厅里电视机正播放着当地新闻。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:18
translate chinese lisa0_f4abcc94:

    # "I pop my head in and see Lisa sitting on the couch alone, watching with her fist in her mouth and tears in her eyes."
    "我探头进去，看见丽莎独自坐在沙发上，一边看着电视，一边把手捂在嘴边，眼中含着泪水。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:21
translate chinese lisa0_29614313:

    # pc "Is everything okay?"
    pc "“一切都还好吗？”"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:22
translate chinese lisa0_2e57e50b:

    # "Lisa startles at my voice and turns, motioning me to come sit next to her."
    "丽莎被我的声音吓了一跳，转过身来，示意我坐到她身边。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:25
translate chinese lisa0_57c2c4c0:

    # sp "I don't know. They said that they found a body in the lake. They haven't said anything else about it."
    sp "我不知道。他们说在湖里发现了一具尸体。除此之外没说别的。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:26
translate chinese lisa0_bf28e1a1:

    # pc "Oh."
    pc "哦。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:27
translate chinese lisa0_e8fad33f:

    # sp "Oh God, I hope it's not your father. I don't know what I'd do."
    sp "天啊，希望不是你父亲。我真不知道该怎么办。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:29
translate chinese lisa0_dacdc92d:

    # "She puts her arms around me and leans her head against my shoulder, tears soaking into my t-shirt."
    "她搂住我，把头靠在我的肩膀上，眼泪浸透了我的T恤。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:30
translate chinese lisa0_c0e958bb:

    # pc "Let's wait and see if they say anything else. It's probably not him."
    pc "“咱们先等等看他们会不会说点别的。八成不是他。”"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:31
translate chinese lisa0_f981c957:

    # sp "They said that they were going to talk about it, but then they started talking about sports."
    sp "“他们本来要说这个事的，结果却开始聊起体育了。”"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:32
translate chinese lisa0_46d1c4b7:

    # sp "Who gives a shit about sports?"
    sp "“谁在乎体育啊？”"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:33
translate chinese lisa0_c5d4ed79:

    # "I put my arm around her shoulder and hold her there until the newscasters finally start talking about the story that had her so worked up."
    "我搂住她的肩膀，就这样抱着她，直到新闻主播终于开始报道那个让她如此焦虑的新闻。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:34
translate chinese lisa0_1a0e9286:

    # "News Anchor" "A sad story today coming out of Carpenter's Bluffs."
    "News Anchor" "今天来自卡彭特崖的一则悲伤消息。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:35
translate chinese lisa0_b07c79d6:

    # "News Anchor" "The body of a seven-year-old girl was pulled out of Lake Daniel today. It's believed that she drowned."
    "News Anchor" "今天，一名七岁女孩的遗体被从丹尼尔湖打捞上来。据信她是溺水身亡。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:37
translate chinese lisa0_4712dd31:

    # sp "Oh, thank God."
    sp "哦，谢天谢地。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:38
translate chinese lisa0_7e1f8bdb:

    # sp "I mean, it's horrible that this girl drowned. I feel so bad for the parents. But I'm so relieved that it wasn't your father."
    sp "我是说，这个女孩溺水身亡真的很可怕。我为她的父母感到非常难过。但我松了一口气，因为那不是你父亲。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:40
translate chinese lisa0_832250a2:

    # sp "Does that make me a bad person?"
    sp "这样想是不是很坏？"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:47
translate chinese lisa0_5b7eede0:

    # sp "I feel horrible. I heard that they had found a body on the radio on the way home from work and all I could think about was them pulling your father's body out of that lake."
    sp "我感觉糟透了。下班回家路上听广播说发现了尸体，我脑子里满脑子想的都是他们把你爸爸的尸体从湖里打捞出来的情景。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:48
translate chinese lisa0_4a8505ff:

    # sp "I just want him to come home."
    sp "我只想让他回家。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:49
translate chinese lisa0_d457cf73:

    # pc "I know, me too."
    pc "我知道，我也是。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:51
translate chinese lisa0_e4d28bf7:

    # "The news is talking about sports and she sits, frustrated, sobbing quietly, her shoulders quivering."
    "电视里播着体育新闻，她坐在那里，满心沮丧，默默抽泣，肩膀微微颤抖。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:52
translate chinese lisa0_652f2570:

    # "Then the news anchor comes on."
    "接着，新闻主播出现了。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:53
translate chinese lisa0_1a0e9286_1:

    # "News Anchor" "A sad story today coming out of Carpenter's Bluffs."
    "News Anchor" "今天来自卡彭特崖的一则悲伤消息。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:54
translate chinese lisa0_b07c79d6_1:

    # "News Anchor" "The body of a seven-year-old girl was pulled out of Lake Daniel today. It's believed that she drowned."
    "News Anchor" "今天，一名七岁女孩的遗体被从丹尼尔湖打捞上来。据信她是溺水身亡。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:56
translate chinese lisa0_4712dd31_1:

    # sp "Oh, thank God."
    sp "哦，谢天谢地。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:57
translate chinese lisa0_3fec87b7:

    # "After this, she practically collapses, falling onto the couch crying."
    "听到这里，她几乎瘫倒在地，跌坐在沙发上哭了起来。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:62
translate chinese lisa0_388aa2a0:

    # "I go sit on the couch next to her and put my hand on her leg. She startles a bit and looks up at me."
    "我走到她身旁的沙发上坐下，把手放在她的腿上。她微微一惊，抬头看着我。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:63
translate chinese lisa0_fa75bbc3:

    # pc "Are you okay?"
    pc "你还好吗？"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:66
translate chinese lisa0_979ec6b9:

    # "Then she stands up and wrapped her arms around me, crying into my shoulder."
    "接着她站起身，双臂环住我，把脸埋在我肩头哭了起来。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:67
translate chinese lisa0_3a8c04ee:

    # sp "Oh [pcname]. I heard on the radio on the way home that they had found a body in the lake."
    sp "哦 [pcname]。我回家路上在广播里听到湖里发现了一具遗体。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:68
translate chinese lisa0_d8fada48:

    # sp "I thought for sure that it was going to be your father. All I could think about was them pulling him out of that lake."
    sp "我当时还以为那肯定是你的爸爸。我满脑子都在想他们把他从湖里打捞出来的场景。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:69
translate chinese lisa0_eb42ef9d:

    # sp "I feel horrible for the family of that little girl, but also so relieved that it wasn't him."
    sp "我为那个小女孩的家人感到难过，但同时也松了一口气，因为那不是他。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:70
translate chinese lisa0_4a8505ff_1:

    # sp "I just want him to come home."
    sp "我只想让他回家。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:71
translate chinese lisa0_0437bdda:

    # pc "I know. Me too."
    pc "我知道。我也是。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:73
translate chinese lisa0_3ebc1e66:

    # "I really don't want to deal with this."
    "我真的不想面对这些。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:74
translate chinese lisa0_e7176023:

    # "I sneak past her and head up to my room, feeling a little bad about it."
    "我悄悄从她身边溜过去，上楼回自己房间，心里有点过意不去。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:80
translate chinese lisa0_bdd243f5:

    # sp "Well, crisis averted for now. Back to just worrying about him constantly."
    sp "嗯，眼下的危机暂时解除了。又回到了无时无刻不在担心他的状态。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:81
translate chinese lisa0_960d3968:

    # "She pulls back and wipes her eyes before straightening her back and recomposing herself."
    "她松开手擦了擦眼睛，然后挺直背脊，重新整理好情绪。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:82
translate chinese lisa0_3a601a62:

    # sp "I don't feel like cooking tonight. How does Chinese delivery sound?"
    sp "今晚我不想做饭。叫中餐外卖怎么样？"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:83
translate chinese lisa0_8a4e8f18:

    # pc "Sounds great to me."
    pc "听起来不错。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:84
translate chinese lisa0_17107884:

    # sp "I'll order something for us, and you can tell me all about your day."
    sp "我来点餐，你再跟我说说你今天过得怎么样。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:85
translate chinese lisa0_1f01ca05:

    # "She calls in the order and we sit and chat afterwards while waiting for it to show up."
    "她打电话点了餐，之后我们坐着聊天，等着外卖送来。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:86
translate chinese lisa0_fe09c3bf:

    # "I tell her all about school and my new job and everything."
    "我跟她讲了学校的事、新工作，还有其他各种事情。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:88
translate chinese lisa0_b202d8fe:

    # sp "Wow, you got so much done in a single day. That's pretty amazing!"
    sp "“哇，你一天就做了这么多事，真了不起！”"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:89
translate chinese lisa0_dd988e66:

    # "She tells me about her day. She is the manager for the helpdesk of an insurance company, with a small team of people underneath her."
    "她也跟我讲了她的近况。她在一家保险公司担任客服部经理，手下有一支小团队。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:90
translate chinese lisa0_f9e557b5:

    # "It isn't a job that she loves, isn't really what she wants to do with her life, but it paid the bills enough when it had been both her and Dad."
    "这不是她热爱的工作，也不是她真正想做的事，但在她和爸爸都还在的时候，这份工作至少能维持生计。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:91
translate chinese lisa0_4127ee35:

    # "Without his income however, she is worried about how she is going to keep the house, the car, and pay for all the utilities."
    "不过，没有了他的收入，她很担心该怎么维持房租、车贷，以及支付所有的水电费。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:92
translate chinese lisa0_4f98b5f9:

    # pc "Maybe I could help some?"
    pc "也许我能帮点忙？"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:93
translate chinese lisa0_6c559b87:

    # sp "Oh no, I couldn't ask you to do that. You are always welcome here. You never have to pay rent. I'm just happy you're here."
    sp "哦不，我不能让你这么做。你随时都欢迎住在这里。你永远不用付房租。只要你在这里，我就很开心。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:94
translate chinese lisa0_fe4fee11:

    # pc "Well I'm at least going to help out around the house then. What could I do?"
    pc "那我至少可以帮忙做些家务。我能做些什么呢？"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:96
translate chinese lisa0_fa250b58:

    # sp "Well the lawn really needs to be mowed. That's all I can think of right now, but if I think of anything else, I'll let you know."
    sp "草坪真的很需要修剪了。目前我只想到这个，但如果我想到了别的，我会告诉你的。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:97
translate chinese lisa0_930771f0:

    # pc "I'll get everything fixed. Promise."
    pc "我会把一切都处理好的。我保证。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:98
translate chinese lisa0_cf109e47:

    # sp "You're the best. Thank you."
    sp "你真是太好了。谢谢你。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:100
translate chinese lisa0_6e7abadd:

    # sp "I can't think of anything right now honey, but thank you."
    sp "亲爱的，我现在想不出什么事，但谢谢你。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:101
translate chinese lisa0_2bb585f4:

    # pc "Anything you need, anything at all, just ask me okay? I'm here to help you out."
    pc "无论你需要什么，无论什么事，只要告诉我，好吗？我就在这里帮你。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:102
translate chinese lisa0_9ff5fd48:

    # "Lisa smiles, tears in her eyes."
    "丽莎微笑着，眼中含着泪。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:103
translate chinese lisa0_b7cc7411:

    # sp "I really couldn't ask for a better person in my life. That goes both ways, okay? If there's anything that I can help you with, you be sure to tell me too."
    sp "我这辈子真的找不到比你更好的人了。这可是双向的，好吗？如果有任何我能帮上忙的事，你一定要告诉我。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:104
translate chinese lisa0_8ce61eb8:

    # "I nod."
    "我点点头。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:105
translate chinese lisa0_5bc44b07:

    # pc "I will."
    pc "我会的。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:106
translate chinese lisa0_f1319eeb:

    # "Finally, when the Chinese food is delivered, we eat in front of the television, then say our goodnights and I head up to my bedroom, completely exhausted after what felt like a very long day."
    "终于，中餐送到了，我们在电视机前吃完饭，互道晚安后，我便上楼回卧室了。这一天感觉漫长得令人筋疲力尽。"

translate chinese strings:

    # game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:2
    old "Lisa has been very emotional lately."
    new "丽莎最近情绪很波动。"

    # game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:3
    old "Check on her when she's in the living room on weekday evenings"
    new "工作日的晚上，当她在客厅时去看看她"

    # game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:20
    old "Check on her"
    new "去看看她"

    # game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:42
    old "I don't think so."
    new "我觉得没必要。"

    # game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:44
    old "A little maybe?"
    new "有一点？"

    # game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:60
    old "Go comfort her"
    new "去安慰她"

    # game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:72
    old "Ignore her"
    new "无视她"

